                                             Steps to build and install an apk file in the mobile

There are two ways to install an apk file:
1. Using the USB cable
2. Build the apk

-> Using the USB cable:
    - Connect your mobile to pc/laptop through the USB cable
    - Open developer options in your mobile
    - Enable USB debugging in the developer option
    - Then your mobile is connected with the android studio
    - Now select your mobile model name and run the app
    - It will install the app and you can check the app in your mobile

-> Build the apk:
    - You can see build option in the menu of android studio
    - Click on the build option
    - Then select Build Bundle(s)/Apk(s) option
    - Then select Build Apk option
    - Now you will get the apk file and install it to your mobile
